snippet.title: Code 7 – gamescom Trailer
snippet.description:
What would you do if you are trapped on a sinister space station with nothing but a computer? Find out as you play the hacker Alex and help your partner Sam to find you and uncover the horrible truth of the facility.

Play Code 7 at gamescom at the Indie Arena Booth, Hall 10.1
